    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and fading clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car starts right up and runs well, though it may require some routine suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 22000.0,
